item.title: How do i fix this(help,look)
item.dc:creator: @Java_Is_My_Bitch Java Is My Bitch™
item.description:
@Java_Is_My_Bitch wrote:

You can start by the ItemIds you’ve edited/added onto item.cfg Or any changes/additions you’ve made to ANY configuration files. Once there, highlight the whole part, open up notepad, and paste it there.

Then press CTRL-F, search for this : " " Without quotes of course. It’s a space, and keep pressing next.

Note: Do not concern yourself on the spaces after and before the equal sign: E.G:

item =

GL.
